OL,3,CFormer teacher denies murder and
OL,4,Csexual assault of baby he planned to
OL,5,Cadopt
OL,7,FA former high school teacher has
OL,8,Fdenied the murder and sexual assault
OL,9,Fof a baby boy he planned to adopt.
OL,11,FJamie Varley appeared at Preston Crown
OL,12,FCourt via video link from the city's
OL,13,Fprison and replied "not guilty" to 33
OL,14,Fcharges relating to 13-month-old
OL,15,FPreston Davey.
OL,17,FThe 36-year-old was in the process of
OL,18,Fadopting Preston with his co-accused
OL,19,FJohn McGowan-Fazakerley, 32, who also
OL,20,Fappeared at the same hearing by video
OL,21,Flink from HMP Durham.
