OL,7,FBoth men spoke only to confirm their
OL,8,Fidentities and deny the charges.
OL,10,FVarley, who worked at South Shore
OL,11,FAcademy school in Blackpool, is also
OL,12,Faccused of multiple counts of assault,
OL,13,Fcruelty and indecent images all
OL,14,Frelating to the baby, Preston Davey.
OL,16,FHe denies the murder and manslaughter
OL,17,Fof Preston on 27 July 2023.
