OL,3,CFormer teacher denies murder and
OL,4,Csexual assault of baby he planned to
OL,5,Cadopt
OL,7,FHe has also pleaded not guilty to two
OL,8,Fcounts of assault by penetration, five
OL,9,Fcounts of cruelty, and one count of
OL,10,Fgrievous bodily harm.
OL,12,FHe denies 12 counts of taking an
OL,13,Findecent photo of a child, two counts
OL,14,Fof making an indecent photo of a
OL,15,Fchild, and one count of distributing
OL,16,Fan indecent photo of a child.
OL,18,FAll the charges, involving still
OL,19,Fimages and videos, relate to Preston
OL,20,FDavey and are alleged to have occurred
OL,21,Fbetween March and July 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
