OL,4,Csexual assault of baby he planned to
OL,5,Cadopt
OL,7,FPreston's mother sat sobbing in the
OL,8,Fpublic gallery of the courtroom as the
OL,9,Fcharges were read out.
OL,11,FJudge Robert Altham, Honorary Recorder
OL,12,Fof Preston, said: "I can only imagine
OL,13,Fhow challenging that was for Preston's
OL,14,Fmother to hear. I'm sorry, but it does
OL,15,Fhave to be done."
OL,17,FVarley also denies seven counts of
OL,18,Fpossession of extreme pornography,
OL,19,Fbetween 2017 and July 2023.
