OL,5,Cadopt
OL,7,FHe is also jointly charged with
OL,8,FMcGowan-Fazakerley with one count of
OL,9,Fthe sexual assault of Preston Davey,
OL,10,Fwhich he denies.
OL,12,FHis co-accused pleaded not guilty to
OL,13,Fthe same offence and also denies two
OL,14,Fcounts of cruelty and one count of
OL,15,Fallowing the death of a child.
OL,17,FThe hearing, on Monday 13 October,
OL,18,Fdealt with administrative matters
OL,19,Fahead of a trial scheduled for April
OL,20,F2026.
