OL,7,FJudge Altham remanded both men, who
OL,8,Flived in Grimsargh, near Preston, into
OL,9,Fcustody ahead of a pre-trial hearing
OL,10,Fon 30 January 2026.
OL,12,FA police investigation first began
OL,13,Fafter officers were called to
OL,14,FBlackpool Victoria Hospital at 7.15pm
OL,15,Fon 27 July 2023, after the baby was
OL,16,Fbrought in unresponsive.
OL,18,FPreston was announced dead shortly
OL,19,Fafter.
